{
  "texts": [
    "The efficiency of completion is computed as follows:",
    "Efficiency (E) = # Task Completion Rate # Total Execution Time Balanced Agent Utilization Score (B).",
    "This metric assesses the distribution of workload among agents, aiming for a balanced utilization where each agent's active running time is similar.",
    "The ideal state is one where no single agent is either overburdened or underutilized.",
    "Here, n is the number of agents, t ∈ R n, t i represents the active running time of agent i, and t is the average active running time across all agents."
  ]
}